05/08/87  endpoints_listening, epl

Syntax as an active request:  [epl]


Syntax as a request:  epl


Function: When invoked as an active request, returns true if the login
server is listening to any endpoints; returns false otherwise.  When
invoked as a request, prints the number of endpoints to which the login
server is listening.


Notes: The list_endpoints requests prints the names of endpoints to
which the login server is listening.
